title: The Oxford illustrated history of the Vikings.pdf
description:

This hook, by leading international scholars, considers the latest research and presents an authoritative account of the Vikings and their age. Excavations as far apart as Dublin and Newfoundland, York and Russia, provide fascinating archaeological evidence, expertly interpreted in this extensively illustrated hook
